> # vancouverLotPlex.R
> # R code to see if 33 vs 50 price gap explains duplex takeup
> # And correlation with price per square foot
> # And Conley stuff
> # Tom Davidoff 
> # 05/05/26
> 
> library(DBI)
> library(RSQLite)
> library(data.table)
> library(fixest)
> library(ggplot2)
> library(duckdb)
> library(sf)
Linking to GEOS 3.13.0, GDAL 3.8.5, PROJ 9.5.1; sf_use_s2() is TRUE
